description: It´s not so easy to surprise me anymore - but this guy was special. I met him on the street and I literally had to run after him as he didn´t hear me at all. When I finally got his attention I found out that he was heading to work. He was a fitness-trainer who just moved to Prague recently. He originally came from Liberec, a city in North-west Bohemia of about 100,000 inhabitants. And as he didn´t have an apartment yet he was living with his granny. And when I asked him about friends he stated that his granny was his best friend.... the cutest thing I´ve ever heard from boys here in Prague. Anyway I told him about a friend who has a model-agency and if he would be ok if I would make some casting-pictures. So we went to his granny´s place...
title: Czech Hunter 223
